description: The tower is old and crumbling, with steep stairs that make you nervous.

name: pool
description: The pool is shallow and small.

name: green shrubbery
description: Somebody took a really good care of the green shrubbery! Some shrubs look like animals

name: desert
description: The desert holds many secrets as it is known to be notoriously hard to navigate.

name: shiny coins from the bottom of the pool
description: Coins found of incalculable value their composition of gold makes them even more valuable

name: pomegranate trees from birds dropping seeds
description: Burdened with fruit, the tree's branches dip towards the ground, offering a nice place to rest.

name: beer keg
description: The keg is large and filled with beer.

name: skulls
description: A worn and bleached skull.

name: amethyst
description: The amethyst sparkled and winked in the light. Its purple shade is rare, making it a treasure to anyone who finds it.

name: pile of discarded armor
description: The discarded armor seems to have something of value to it.

name: long, wooden table
description: The table is worn and yet sturdy, its wood splintering at points but display its history proudly.

name: fairy lights
description: The fairy light sparkled in the night, its beauty obvious even to your untrained eye.

name: pots
description: The dusty, clay pot is artistically crafted into the form of a slender woman, seductive and enchanting to behold.

name: plates
description: the plate is exceptionally colorful and interesting

name: mugs
description: The engravings on the mugs detail the ancient battles of heroes.

name: wide variety of grains, vegetables and fruits
description: The grain is harvested by the farmers and then sold at the market. It is a major part of the diets of the townspeople.

name: pitchforks
description: The pitchfork is old and rusted. There are cobwebs between the tines, as if it hasn't been used in many years.

name: wheelbarrows
description: This wheelbarrow is in rusted condition, but should be fine for transporting items.

name: pen
description: This pen is very old and has ink stains on the side.

name: clothes line
description: The clothes line appears to be made of synthetic fibers than cotton. It's strong enough to hold a man, but delicate enough to dry one's clothing.

name: chicken coop
description: The chicken coop looks well tended, the wood freshly painted and the wire free of rust.

name: diamonds
description: A precious gem. Rare and expensive used for jewelry.

name: comfortable cushion
description: A cushion that is comfortable to sit on or rest against.

name: large pet lion
description: The large pet lion looks fierce.

name: king's flagon
description: The king's flagon is silver with intricate engravings portraying his kingdom.

name: ritual knife
description: A knife used in rituals by people. Very decorative and intricate.

name: chalice
description: The chalice is made of solid gold. It appears to have some wine stains along the rim.

name: pikes
description: A metal weapon sharpened to a point on the end of a long pole.

name: spear
description: The warriors carry similar long spears with a diamond tipped point for battle.

name: armor
description: The armor is well worn, not old, but seemingly used a great deal.

name: mace
description: The mace is sturdy and strong. You would hate to be hit by the metal spikes that line its head.

name: flail
description: The flail is solid and heavy, its weight an indicator of the damage it is capable of.

name: pew
description: The pew is dusty and is cool to the touch.

name: pulpit
description: The pulpit is made of fine wood and has papers of the old priests speeches on it

name: tithe plate
description: A shallow plate, but wrapped in gold, the tithe plate serves to host the devious church goers offerings.

name: tempior market
description: you've visited the market several times, and recognize its lively disposition.

name: finest wines
description: The wine is smooth and dry.

name: market
description: The market is full of wares from around the world.

name: tavern
description: The tavern is lively and full of drunken patrons.

name: ale
description: The ale is dark, foamy, and tastes bitter.

name: bar stools
description: The old wooden bar stool at the tavern was carved out of the old pine trees that stood where the church now lies.

name: large bed
description: The large bed had seven pillows on it.

name: wooden headboard
description: The wooden headboard is beginning to lose its smooth shine, and there are two circular fade marks right where one's head might be.

name: fancy roof
description: The roof of the building is incredible to behold. It is covered in carvings and patterns which you'd never seen before.

name: large tapestry
description: The tapesty is big and can cover a significant part of a wall. It is black and made of a thick fabric.

name: map of the kingdom
description: The map is very old and wrinkled, with one corner slightly torn.  The paper is yellowed.

name: large wooden doors
description: This Large wooden door is grand and new. This door has just been made and painted to be an entrance to the King's quarters.

name: large wardrobe
description: The wardrobe is made from solid oak and stained a rich, dark brown.

name: elegant paintings
description: The painting appears to be of a religious leader. His features are very realistic.

name: decorative swords
description: The decorative sword has gemstones in the handle and isn't particularly sharp.

name: decorative shields
description: The shield had many dents and scratches, the sides were lined with blood.

name: large table with an ordinate cushion for the king's crown
description: The crown is made of solid gold, adorned with the finest gems you have ever laid your eyes on.

name: smoke
description: A lot of smoke is emanating from the fireplace.

name: glitter
description: The glitter sparkles brightly when it is exposed to sunlight

name: feathers
description: the feather is white and very soft

name: courtyard
description: The courtyard is expansive and decorated with beautiful sculptures and fountains.

name: huge pavilion of stone patio
description: The pavillion stands amidst the devastation from the hurricane.

name: shape of a large rectangle
description: The rectangle looks to be the shape of the sword.

name: luscious hedges dotted
description: The hedge is neatly trimmed and watered in the morning

name: roses
description: rose looks special in making bouquet

name: potted flowers
description: The potted flowers are beautiful and added a pop of color to the landscape.

name: stone benches
description: Stone is a solid object

name: fenced garden plots
description: The fenced garden plots are aged by weather with brown fence posts and fertile dirt

name: central atrium
description: The palace's central atrium has a wide assortment of plants, some local and some exotic. Together they create a beautiful aroma that calmed the soul.

name: arcadian garden
description: Walking in this garden makes you want to sing. There are several fountains and lots of different type of flowers

name: summer palace
description: The summer palace is tall and inviting.

name: beautiful courtyard
description: The courtyard is immaculate and is obviously tended by skilled hands. It is filled with many wonderous flowers, the likes of which you'd never seen.

name: gift
description: Wrapped in a magnificent red bow, the purple wrapping on this gift fits smoothly over the box contained inside.

name: tulips
description: The tulips petals are a vibrant hue of red, and the smell radiating off of it is all but enchanting.

name: lavender
description: The lavender is lovely and the smell reminds you of better days.

name: alligators
description: This land dragon might make for some good meat!  Watch out though, it looks like it may fight back.

name: poisonous snakes
description: The poisonous snake has hideous fangs and eyes which are menacing red.

name: brightly colored flowers that grow up to 30 feet tall
description: The stems droop under the weight of the orange flowers that top them.  You find the perfume to be sweetly cloying and unpleasant.

name: homes made from watermelon skins
description: These houses look quite odd with their marbled green texture.  While you're not certain how long these homes would last, their watermelon exteriors make quite an impression.

name: mushrooms
description: the mushroom is sweet and eaten by many

name: large oak tree
description: The large oak tree towers above you, its branches twisted and gnarled.

name: two home made wooden crosses
description: the cross has nails stuck on it.

name: mausoleums
description: The weathered stone on the front facade told of a story of ancient battles and long dead conflicts. The mausoleum has many stories to tell, some of pain, some of peace, all moments of a long dead history.

name: iron gate
description: The gate is ornate, with complicated iron scrollwork patterns.

name: elaborate carpet pieces
description: The carpet piece is beautifully colored with red, purple and silver hues.

name: detailed paintings
description: The detailed paintings were peeled back, revealing maps.

name: wooden pews
description: The pew is weather-worn and splintery.  You don't think it would support your weight.

name: brick walls
description: The brick wall is so old and dirty, it seems to have been here for quite a while.

name: bible
description: The bible is bound by black leather, its pages yellowed by years of use.

name: smells
description: The smell permeating the room is awful.

name: animals
description: Common creatures that inhabit most land. Often hunted as food or kept as pets.

name: grape juice
description: The juice of the grape is sweet to drink.

name: outside temple
description: The temple has blood on the floor leading to the doorway.

name: lush green trees
description: the tree is strong and tall, it is full of life and a unique green color

name: beautiful blossoming jasmine flowers
description: The beautiful blossoming jasmine flower shows its delicate white petals extending off its gentle brown stem.

name: pink and white outline
description: The outline of the object, pink and white in color, remained on the ground.

name: place
description: The place is abandoned, but you can hear echoes of its previous history.

name: entrance
description: everyone comes in through the entrance of building.

name: mountain
description: The mountain is tall and its peak is coated in a fresh, white fall of snow.

name: front door
description: the front door has let in many different people over the years

name: rare wood from a tree that doesn't exist anymore
description: The wood seems very unique in its attributes.

name: lush tapestries
description: The Lush tapestry is clearly woven with great care. Each silk thread has it's own unique purpose, and together they form a beautiful depiction of kings of old.

name: wooden stool
description: The stool is old and uneven.

name: stone carvings
description: The carving appears to be of language of its own, unfamiliar to anyone in the kingdom. To know it, would be to know the story these markings are hiding in plain sight.

name: building
description: The building towers before you, stretching so high it looks like it reaches the clouds.

name: earth
description: The earth is round and vast. It has many lands and bodies of water.

name: kettle
description: The kettle has a large dent on one side, and is scratched in a few places.

name: small bed
description: A source of comfort for weary, this bed has layers of woolen blankets, and a straw mattress.

name: dirty wooden bucket
description: The rickety bucket's contents have been removed, leaving a filthy residue.

name: desk
description: The desk is made of sturdy oak but is very low to the floor.

name: desk chair
description: The desk chair is well worn. It is clear someone spent many a days completing work while sitting there.

name: room
description: Don't forget that if you ask for a room in a castle you may get your wish and end up in a dungeon cell.

name: pictures
description: the picture is very beautifully framed.

name: polished gold
description: A beautiful goblet of gold. It is quite heavy in the hand and looks to have been made by a master of their craft.

name: long table
description: A long oaken table set up in the dining hall. There are many burns and cuts in it's surface.

name: pictures trimmed in gold
description: The picture seems to have an elegant gold trim around it.

name: gold silverware
description: On further inspection of the gold silverware you notice that it has the King's initials engraved on each piece.

name: boulder
description: The boulder is heavy and dusty with moss growing on the side.

name: cattle
description: This cattle has a shiny red coat with white spots across it.

name: cows grazing
description: The cows grazing contently in the green field belied the fierce battle that was approaching.

name: barrels for crops
description: The barrel is made out of oak and supposed to hold crops for the week.

name: hoe for digging
description: Looks like nobody ever used this hoe for digging. It looks brand new and has no stains

name: watering bucket
description: The bucket's many holes, cracks and splintered panels were all signs indicating that it had long outlived its usefulness to the farmer.

name: summit
description: It's foggy and the air is thin at this place. There are bones lining the pathway to the very top, it would seem a lot have parished travelling through here.

name: dirty trail
description: The trail is long, winding, and covered in mud.

name: streams
description: The stream flows quietly, twisting and turning its way about.

name: largest trash heap
description: It is a mountain of disgusting and putrid trash.

name: wooden chair with one leg broken
description: The chair has one broken leg, and there are still jagged splinters where the missing leg used to be.

name: crossbow with no string
description: The crossbow is made of wood and broken from being used in combat too much

name: rag doll with the head detached
description: The rag doll is dressed like a peasant but the head has been torn off from a fit of rage.

name: mattresses
description: All of the mattresses are stiff and lumpy, providing no comfort.

name: gallows
description: The gallows is an ominous sight for all who passed by it. A large contraption of wood and rope with only one purpose. Hanging.

name: priceless painting of past kings
description: The painting details the kings crown very well

name: vaulted ceiling
description: The vaulted ceiling is so large and open that it is almost suffocating.

name: banners
description: The banner is faded and stained, appearing to be well past its prime.

name: colorful tapestries
description: The tapestry is dusty and old, with exquisite stitches in the shape of a dragon

name: large stone fireplace
description: The fireplace is large and made of grey stone.

name: double thick wooden door
description: After looking closely this door is a double door and it is made of wood.

name: floor to ceiling mirror
description: The tall mirror stretches from the floor to the ceiling, clearly displaying your reflection.

name: heavy blanket
description: The heavy blanket is incredibly comfortable.

name: ornate chairs
description: With hand-carved lion faces and coat of arms and a frame made of solid mahogany the ornate chair is fit for royalty.

name: bones of the innocent
description: These poor innocent bones, they deserve a proper burial.

name: mudpit
description: The mud pit is bubbling slightly, as if gases from underground are being released.

name: vegetation
description: the vegetation is overgrown with weeds and grass.

name: carcasses
description: The deer carcass has been badly torn.  You do not want to encounter whatever destroyed the creature.

name: pieces of fortune
description: The scroll contains sacred text that may influence the fortune of those who wield the scrolls, and it's gold text shines in the sunlight.

name: legendary swords
description: The sword is very old, you would assume it had once belonged to a legendary warrior.

name: pieces of armor
description: The piece of armor is polished to a dazzling shine.  It is unscratched and flawless.

name: magical crystal
description: The magical crystal is round and glowing.  It emits a white light.

name: gold coins
description: This coin has been worn down and is slightly corroded, as if it has spent time in a river.

name: tapestries depicting battles won
description: The tapestry was stained with the blood of enemies and used as a reminder of the dangers of war

name: 80-foot tall bronze statue of an 8 legged goddess
description: The deity seems to stare into the distance, the mere mortals bellow her not worthy of her gaze.

name: money
description: The small, tarnished coin is imprinted with a seal you don't recognize.

name: painting and works of art of the goddess,
description: The works of art depict the goddess in flowing robes and a crown of gold. The painting is oil on canvas inside a gilded frame.

name: tapestries of important historical value,
description: The tapestry has many colors and displayed a historical scene.

name: ornate tables
description: The table is very ornate and beautiful.

name: rope bridge
description: The ancient rope bridge appears fragile and rickety, swaying to and fro in the wind.  The bridge floor is made of planks of rotting wood which, if stepped through, would abruptly pull the victim down to an unsuspecting death.

name: babbling brook
description: The babbling brook flows gently over rocks. This brook supplies my horses and crops with water.

name: horse tack
description: The horse tack is made of hardened leather and molded iron. It is designed perfectly to fit a horse.

name: hay shovels
description: the hay shovel is new but heavily used. there are remnants of matter other than hay, indicaitng the owner's have gottent their money's worth

name: water troughs
description: The wooden trough is broken from holding the heavy water and grass

name: medicines
description: The medicine is a dark brown color, and looks like it tastes disgusting.

name: bee hive
description: There is a gentle buzzing or humming sound coming from the beehive, and a few bees can be seen coming and going from it.

name: small gazebo
description: This small place is perfect for merryiment and joy.

name: lamp posts
description: The lamp post has nicks and scratches on it. From what, nobody knows.

name: trash bins
description: The trash bins are in a row, some appeared empty.

name: park benches
description: The bench is made of smooth stone and is comfortable when you sit on it.

name: variety of drapes
description: The drape is heavy and course but as a covering, you can use it as protection from the cold.

name: antlers on the wall
description: The antlers have many points on them. They are mounted on a piece of carved wood.

name: rusty gate
description: The marking etched into the rusty gate reveal its history and tells its story.

name: runes
description: the runes are hard

name: dirty and grimy floor
description: The dirty and grimy floor has drinks spilled on it.

name: puddle of water
description: The puddle is shallow and full of dirty water.

name: torch
description: The torch is stained brown from all the times it was lit.

name: wooden fence
description: The fence is made of wood and seems very sturdy.

name: plow
description: The plow is in need of repair, and looks like it hasn't been used for many years.

name: rake
description: The rake is well worn and missing some of its long grabbing teeth.

name: silver
description: The shiny silver looks valuable to you, either as currency or as a raw material.

name: sapphire
description: The sapphire is beautiful.  The gem emits a dark blue light.

name: chair
description: The chair is sturdy, but uncomfortable to sit on. It had no cushioning of any kind.

name: rectory
description: The rectory's gray stone walls are covered in lichens.  Its wooden door sits askew, but its windows sparkle in the sun.

name: beds
description: The bed is elevated off the ground, but still shows signs that something had chewed through it.

name: crosses displayed on the walls
description: The cross is simple and made of iron.

name: altars where they kneel in prayer
description: The altar is ornate and highly polished. The woodwork gleams.

name: goddess
description: The goddess is plump and unadorned and her skin is as smooth as polished bronze.

name: pair of headphones
description: The headphones are made from shells of coconut and wired together using strands of straw.

name: paddles
description: the paddle is marked up and splintery. it has several markings from fish teeth, some large enough to be sharks

name: trapdoor
description: The evil lord had a trapdoor installed in his great room.

name: underground plant-life
description: A plant the has various forms. Found in caves and mines that has a sense of mystery to it.

name: worms
description: The worm is motionless and black, and you're not sure if it is still alive.

name: knocker
description: The brass knocker was grimy and worn from the years of use.

name: rivets
description: The rivet is made of metal. It may be useful for binding objects together.

name: archway
description: The archway is tight and dark and may clearly contains hidden dangers.

name: ancient tomes
description: The ancient tome contain powerful magic. The spell inside can be use to control someone.

name: scrolls
description: The scroll is beautifully illustrated with the coat of arms.

name: jars of mysterious reagents
description: The jar was old and bore markings in a strange, unknown language.

name: magical lights
description: The shimmering magical light glistens of shades of blue and green from afar

name: old paintings
description: The painting is very old. It is dusty and has cobwebs stuck to it.

name: old statues
description: The statue is cracked and dirty. It seems to be very old.

name: papers littering the floor
description: The paper is yellow from the tarnish of time, several rips and tears along it's imperfect edges.

name: flasks
description: The small flasks contain a liquid that could only be described as intoxicating.

name: pen
description: Made from a goose feather, the end has been whittled into a point and is stained with black ink.

name: purses
description: This purse is pretty small. It's made out of alligator skin and it looks pretty old but still has a lot of life left

name: rusty manicals
description: The manical is rusty and stained with blood of whoever has worn them.

name: rusty pegs
description: The orange rust of the peg has peeled off exposing the metal surface.

name: rusty bars
description: Look at those rusty bars, doesn't look like anyone has been using them for a while.

name: dusty floor
description: The dusty floor looks dirty to everyone.

name: red silk prayer bench
description: The bench is used for prayer and is covered with a lovely red silk fabric.

name: red and white candles
description: the candle has very bright light

name: prayer book
description: The book contains many prayers. It has many pages and filled with many words on each.

name: single tent
description: This tent looks to be made of waxed linen canvas and, while it is patched in places from much use, has the look of a well cared for shelter.  It would be quite helpful come rain or nightfall.

name: gears
description: the gear is not functional.

name: levers
description: The lever is covered with rust and would be difficult,if not impossible,to pull it in its current state.

name: tree branches
description: The tree branch is wet and rotting. It's so thick, you can barely wrap your hand around it.

name: maps to get out of the lake
description: The map to get out of the lake is made completely out of papyrus.  Written in black ink, its mysterious hieroglyphics and strange markings can be interpreted through a key found on the bottom, left-hand corner.

name: materials
description: The material is lightweight and can be worn in the summer.

name: sheets
description: The bedroom sheets are old and dirty after not being ished for months

name: homespun blankets
description: The blanket is warm and cozy.  It has been made in warm tones.

name: quill
description: The quill is long and black and writes smoothly. It is smooth to touch and the feather is soft.

name: rug
description: The rug is made of patterened wool.

name: simple wooden bucket for holding umbrellas, walking sticks, etc
description: The wooden bucket is well worn. It has been used to carry a variety of items and water over a period of many years.

name: mirror hanging on the wall
description: The mirror is barely reflective with dirt and dust covering it's once shiny surface.

name: green, luscious, rolling hills
description: You can tell the hills are full of life- so green and luscious. They seem to roll on for miles.

name: fruit trees
description: The limbs of the fruit tree sag under the weight of the cumbersome burden.

name: farming equipment
description: The farming equipment is rusted and ragged. The wooden handles are practically nothing but splinters.

name: building wall
description: This wall was built long time ago out of huge stones and clay

name: large field
description: A large fields. Crops are grown here and wild game pass through it.

name: surrounding fence
description: The fence surrounding the castle is obviously designed to keep those inside from getting out rather than the other way around.

name: well
description: the wishing well is dry, which doesn't give one the best sense of having their wishes granted.

name: copper vase
description: The vase is made of copper and has been polished to a high shine.

name: leather cloth
description: The leather cloth smells of fresh cow hide

name: animal skins used as rugs
description: The animal skins were remarkably clean, but came from an animal you did not know.

name: gunpowder
description: The odor of gunpowder penetrates far more than even its dust.  Working with it is almost too difficult a task to be done quickly.

name: helmets
description: The helmet is cracked and dented, but still polished to a pristine shine.

name: floors
description: the floor is wooden

name: brushes
description: Upon close inspection, the brush is dainty and carved with roses.

name: tape
description: The tape is rudimentary but does the job well of holding the bandage in place. You can see a sticky resin on one side of the material.

name: bright buildings
description: The bright building has so many beautiful colors and patterns on it, it stands out so much to notice anything else.

name: merchant stands
description: Look at all these merchant stands, There are so many items to look at!

name: jungle
description: A rainy expanse of tropical trees, plants and poisonous wildlife.

name: grapes
description: The grape is red and juicy and makes you think of summer.

name: chocolate milk
description: The glass of chocolate milk has a slight film on top, as though it has been sitting out for a long time.

name: machines
description: The machine of war is devestating. Large stones sit inside it, waiting to be launched.

name: weapons
description: The weapon looks light and delicate, as though it couldn't really hurt anyone.

name: pamphlets
description: The pamphlet is made out of paper and has a lot of information inside it.

name: heavy trunk
description: The trunk is heavy and the wood painted a deep black. It has a gold lock on it, and you cann't help but wonder what treasures it contained.

name: racks of plain clothing
description: the clothing is long and colorful.

name: polishing cloth
description: The polishing cloth is covered in dark polish.  It is tattered and frayed as though it has been used for several years.

name: clothes brushes
description: The cloth was clean and bright in all its colors, stealing it comes to mind.

name: plush mattress
description: The mattress is stained and smelly as if it has been stuck in a barn for ages.

name: pans
description: The pan is rusty, not having been ished in sometime

name: napkins
description: The napkin is filthy with old food and wine stains.

name: medicine
description: The is so much medicine, you can barely pick which one you need. Perhaps you don't need any of it....

name: cell phone
description: A curious dull colored object that seems to come to life and glow at random times.

name: computer
description: The computer, also known as an abacus, is a wooden square with faded paint delicately holding metal rods and sliding beads.

name: bones of unlucky spelunkers
description: The bone is brittle and almost broken from being trampled on too many times.

name: giant club
description: On further inspection of the giant club you notice it was stained with blood from the battle at the castle earlier.

name: giant firepit
description: The firepit is made of large stones.  Dead grass fills the center.

name: headstones
description: Here are the headstones, in this sacred field, where lie the heroes who gave their lives, so that this kingdom would survive before the fiefs that wanted to plunder it and take advantage of its wealth.

name: mausoleum
description: The mausoleum is shrouded in fog and you think you hear strange noises from within.

name: shovels
description: The shovel has a wooden handle and a metal bottom. The handle has some blood stained on it and the metal is weather beaten.

name: seat
description: The seat is dirty with the blood from the farmers.

name: golden trim
description: The trim is beautiful and expensive. You wonder who would wear something like this.

name: golden cloth
description: The cloth is gold and shimmers when moved in light.

name: prayer beads
description: The prayer beads are made of wood and look well worn.

name: baubles
description: The bauble is no bigger than a pebble, but it's shiny glow gives it an ornate appearance.

name: old pictures
description: The picture on the wall shows a likeness of a rotund man with a full, bushy beard riding a horse.

name: travelers
description: The traveler is wearing ragged cloth shoes, a torn smock and a cap embellished with the feather of a hawk.

name: crow bar
description: The crow bar is shiny and beutiful, it is made out of a weird metal alloy.

name: bat
description: The bat appears to be from a coat of arms.

name: small metal bucket
description: The metal bucket appears to be made of copper, with multiple dents and scratches on the the surface.

name: bars
description: The bars of gold have a wonderful glow, even though they have been hidden for years.

name: blanket
description: The blanket is made from thick cotton, and it is a dull red color.

name: food tray
description: A simple tray, to put one's food on.

name: boats floating
description: The boat is old, gnarled, and rotted, and smells of spoiled fish.

name: ropes and other tools
description: An assortment of hemp strands that have been twisted and braided into a strong rope.

name: bait bucket
description: The bucket is raw with the smell of fish, it has darkened with age

name: arrows
description: The arrow is so beat up and dirty, you can see indention's in it.

name: bows
description: This bow has very detailed carvings

name: huge window in the front
description: The large window is clear with minimal distortion.

name: rows of items
description: The row of books on the shelf is aligned neatly with great care.

name: bright colored curtains
description: The curtain is a vivid purple and made of a shiny, soft fabric. You think its owner must be quite extravagant.

name: potions and cures for sale
description: There are potions and cures for sale every morning in the market.

name: church
description: The church is beautifully decorated with floor to ceiling stained glass windows.

name: narrow door
description: The narrow door is large enough only for a child to get through.

name: blue floors
description: The floor has a blue color that is faded because of its old age and lack of upkeep.

name: black ceiling
description: The ceiling is black and made of thick stones.

name: armor set
description: The armor set is heavy and made of iron.  It will protect a body from harm.

name: clouds
description: The cloud is vibrant white with no sign of turbulent weather.

name: fog
description: The fog is heavy and hard to see through.

name: path
description: A path trodden through by some.

name: evergreen trees
description: The evergreen trees line the castle walls, providing a beautiful deep green hue.

name: icicles
description: The icicle is sharp but dull enough at the same time that it cannot be used as a weapon.

name: merchandise
description: The merchandise is unique.  It is homemade for the square.

name: kettles
description: The kettle is warm with boiling water in it.

name: coral reef
description: The reef has majestic colors of green and blue. It is large enough to contain many species.

name: pit-fall trap
description: The pit-fall trap is covered by grass and twigs.  They cover a deep hole beneath.

name: glowing rocks
description: The rock appears to glow in the moonlight, illuminating the path it lines.

name: poisonous plants
description: The poisonous plant has sharp purple thorns and black berries. It is actually beautiful in a dark and twisty way.

name: wrecked ships
description: The ship has almost completely rotted away, clearly having been at this wreck site for a very long time.

name: torn fabric
description: The torn fabric is used as a cloth atop the royal dinner table.

name: thin sticks
description: Thin sticks that may be used to stoke a fire.

name: orange sand
description: The sand is a small grain that sits on top of the horse's neck.

name: campfire
description: The campfire looks warm and inviting.  It gives off a soft glow as the wood crackles and pops cheerfully.

name: spring nearby
description: The spring is gently bubbling, and steam rises off the water.

name: long curtains
description: The curtain is made of a heavy material.  It is long and flowing.

name: marble floor
description: This floor shines as if it has never seen the bottom of a dirty boot.

name: shrubbery
description: The shrubbery stands about waist high. Its thick green foliage conceals a small animal nest.

name: bushes
description: This lush bush has an assortment of birds, nesting in it.

name: lilypad
description: Right now, this lily pad is only the size of a child's fist. Soon, however, it will grow to be several feet wide.

name: algae
description: That algae may look harmless until it starts eating your flesh.

name: brown doors
description: The brown door is tall and intimidating. It is made of thick wood.

name: church guides
description: Church guides are so nice and helpful, you can always talk to them.

name: music organ
description: The organ is severely out of tune, so it must not be used often.

name: coconut tree
description: The coconut tree towers above the tropical landscape.  Heavy coconuts sway with the tree in the breeze.

name: wooden boat parts
description: The wooden boat part is carefully crafted and sanded to the point of being smooth. The lacquer provides a clean shine to it.

name: makeshift stall
description: The quickly made stall was very unstable and not very well built.

name: stones
description: This stone is extremely rough and heavy.

name: gold
description: Fine shiny gold pieces, of great value.

name: clearing
description: The clearing is an open field with a few cut down tree stumps.

name: old pine trees
description: The pine tree is still standing after 700 years and it is easy to see why people continue to watch it.

name: haystacks
description: A large pile of wheat stalks that emit a musty farmyard fragrance.

name: sickle
description: The handle has been worn from use, and the blade is old and caked with dirt. This is a real farmer's tool, not something that's been used as ornamentation.

name: cliff
description: The cliff is a great vantage point to watch over the valley and see any intruders approaching.

name: ocean
description: The ocean is mighty and salty. The waves are really strong and there are some sharks swimming close to the shore

name: drawbridge
description: The drawbridge is old and massive, protecting its surroundings from anyone who dare attempt to cross.

name: torture instrument
description: The spike gleam wickedly and are flecked with dried blood on this torture implement.  You're not quite sure how it is used, but it looks painful.

name: dirty rug
description: The rug was stained with mud from the onslaught of dirty kids that ran over it.

name: dirty chandelier with dust and cobwebs on it
description: The chandelier hangs high on the ceiling, providing light to things below it.

name: rustic tools
description: Hand-held gadgets of the "getting things done" nature.

name: stack of hay
description: It is dry and brittle, more like straw yet you see some mold at the bottom.

name: bits for the horses
description: The horse bit is old and worn.

name: blankets for the stable workers to sleep with
description: The blanket is dirty and stained, and has a musty smell to it.

name: fertilizer
description: The fertilizer is brown and mushy to the touch.

name: altar
description: The alter is sacred and inscribed with religious words.

name: offering plate
description: The offering plate is made of gold and several gold pieces sit atop it already.

name: baptismal
description: The baptismal is rather ornate with strange runes and obsidian accents.

name: sand that is white as snow
description: Whether bleached by the sun or made of white shells, this sand is pristine and unblemished.

name: water that is as clear as a crystal
description: the crystal gem is beautiful.

name: towels
description: The towel is moldy and damp, its usefulness long since passed.

name: huge door lock
description: the door is rusty and dirty.

name: mold and fungus
description: Musty, slimy residue that clings to the surface of all things wet, or habitable.

name: cast iron skillets
description: The black skillet is nicely seasoned, not showing any rusted spots.

name: broken glass
description: The glass is shattered in a hundred pieces, it is sharp and dangerous.

name: gray stones
description: A grey rock that's not useful for much except possibly ammo for a sling.

name: artwork
description: The artwork appears to be expensive and made from drawings of a prestigious painter

name: crack
description: The crack seems basic and unimpressive.

name: rooms
description: The room is dark and the walls are covered in artworks.

name: broken chairs
description: The chair is broken, with the back almost completely separated from the seat.

name: compass
description: The compass is shiny in the sun and felt warm to your touch. Your very survival depends on it for navigation in unknown lands.

name: different types of swords
description: The sword has a clean sharp edge.  It is long and heavy.

name: other types of weapons
description: The weapon is too heavy for you to lift and you wonder who it was made for.

name: spare arrowheads
description: The arrowhead is designed to enter a person's body easily.

name: spare bowstring
description: This bowstring is made from animal gut and smoothed over with beeswax to protect it from the elements.  It seems to be a good replacement, should you need it.

name: lagoon
description: The lagoon is small and almost perfectly round. The water is rippling slightly in the breeze.

name: lily pads
description: The lilypad is a vibrant shade of green. Its roots dangling far below it.

name: body parts
description: The body part is covered in blood and is somewhat soft to the touch.

name: hard bench
description: The hard bench appears to be crafted from solid oak, with a gold base in the shape of bird feet.

name: gold drapes
description: The gold drapes are now tattered and worthless due to the lack of care and upkeep.

name: large dark oak and gold bench
description: The bench is very large and made of oak, and has been decorated with great intricacy. The golden carvings seem to hint at the wealth of its owner.

name: wooden cross
description: The wooden cross is faded in color from being worn too much by the priest

name: forest trees.
description: The tree seems healthy and large. It should prove to be climbable.

name: wood is gathered to make fire
description: The wood lay scorched on the ground, and warm to the touch.

name: new trees planted once a year
description: The tree is deeply knotted and rough to the touch.

name: animals that live in the forest
description: Upon closer look, it seems to be wounded.

name: plants besides the trees, like bushes and grass.
description: The plant was very colorful and came in many shapes and sizes.

name: horse trough
description: The horse trough is already empty and it surprised you.

name: garden plants
description: The plant is lush and bright green. It looks healthy and vibrant.

name: stones with inscriptions on them
description: The stone has ancient ruins inscribed upon them.

name: horse hitch
description: The hitch is heavy and made from the strongest leather.

name: crown
description: Thought of as a holy item, the crown goes only to those who are worthy enough.

name: graves
description: The grave is old enough to have grass growing over it at this point, and the only marker that remains is the engraved stone of the resident.

name: cookpot
description: The cookpot is large, heavy, and round. Peering inside, you have trouble seeing the bottom.

name: shelf
description: The shelf is sturdy and held in place with rusty iron brackets.  It held a collection of vials and potions.  The bottles are dusty and looked like they've been there for years.

name: cross
description: The cross is broken and with a few dents in the sides.

name: harnesses
description: The harness is made of leather and beautiful.

name: precious gems
description: The gem is shiny and bright. The last owner took good care of it.

name: stacks of gold plates
description: The plate is made of glass and is white with a gold rim around it.

name: coins
description: The coin seemed old, rusted, and worthless. However, after closer inspection, you reveal the underlying intricate design of the priceless coin.

name: ancient relics
description: The ancient relic is worn and what was once an intricate depiction of a king is now faded and hard to see.

name: works of art
description: The portrait of the king is an absolute work of art. The depection of him is spot on, and has clearly been painted by a master.

name: crystal chandeliers
description: You feel luxurious simply being in the presence of the intricate crystal chandelier, watching the light glimmer off of one of the many thousand pieces of minuscule glass shards, a piece so elaborate that only the extremely wealthy could afford.

name: ice throne
description: The sword seems to be old but still reliable enough to cut down a animal.

name: ice goblet
description: This goblet is freezing cold to the touch and, while it might keep whatever liquid is inside it very cold, it might also cause your hands to get frostbite.  It seems to shimmer gently as you look upon it.

name: enchanted torches
description: The enchanted torch lit up with a magical purple flame.

name: ancient fossils
description: The fossil is embedded in a piece of shale, and appears to be a small sea creature.

name: magical gems
description: The magical gem pulses a bright red, with swirls of black throughout.

name: timbers
description: The timber appears to be riddled with worm holes.

name: block and tackle
description: The block and tackle could be used to raise something.

name: mine cart
description: The mine cart looks very unsafe, hopefully no one uses it.

name: ore
description: The ore looks like a common rock, unpolished and plain.

name: hammer
description: Such an old hammer. Looks like the handle is about to break, there are several cracks in it. The metal part is still good

name: nails
description: The nail is rusted and worn and is no longer useful.

name: large gate
description: The gate is vast and big, but a bit rusty.

name: barn
description: The barn is huge and red in color!

name: jars
description: The jar seems to have a crack on it. I don't think you can use it anymore.

name: cross
description: the cross is large in size, but made of a lightweight wood. it has nails on the left and right sides, indicating it is religious in nature

name: barrels of beer
description: The beer is a rich amber ale that smells of hops.

name: old broom
description: the broom is very dusty and fragile.

name: wooden table
description: A simple table crafted of rough brown wood.

name: cabinet
description: A cabinet stood out painted pitch black.

name: giant four poster bed
description: A great bed that should offer fine rest.

name: fluffy pillows
description: The pillow holds all the king's secrets within its soft innards and satin cover. If it could talk it would be the perfect agent against the king.

name: fur carpet
description: The carpet is made of an animal's fur.  The carpet is soft and warm.

name: mahogany writing desk
description: Beautiful and dark, the solid rectangular desk has ten drawers, ornate golden pulls and a heavily polished surface.

name: chamber pot
description: Since there is no plumbing in the kingdom, the townspeople have open chamber pots in their homes to excrete waste into.

name: vanity
description: The vanity is made from the finest oak in all the realm. The designs on the sides are of the royal insignia.

name: bright red targets
description: The target is riddled with arrows from others practicing for battle.

name: quiver
description: The quiver contains a mess of arrows, its leather frame stretched from years of use.

name: bow
description: The bow appears to be made of a dark brown wood, its string is taught and straight, and it is about as long as your arm.

name: pile of treasure
description: a pile of treasure has been picked of all other items. it is simply gold, and no jewelry or other valuables

name: chairs
description: Among numerous scratches on its surface, you can make out some marking.

name: torches on the wallls
description: The torch burns bright.  The handle is made from sturdy wood.

name: gold plated dome
description: A giant cross sits atop the gold plated dome.

name: chandeliers
description: The chandelier is full of cobwebs and contains only the small stubs of candles.

name: hand carved 30 person kings dining table
description: A piece of furniture used to set food on while you eat.

name: hand woven rug
description: You admire the colorful pattern of the hand woven rug, with hues of intense blues and greens.

name: palace
description: The palace is ornate and enormous, making you wonder what kind of emperor lives inside.

name: plates that serve the royal members.
description: You know the symbols on the plates to be the crest of the royal family. Only royalty may be served from these plates.

name: jug that holds the wine the servants fill glasses with
description: The jug is very useful for filling glasses of tea at dinner.

name: canopy
description: The canopy is falling apart quite a bit, but some sprucing up should fix it.

name: foliage
description: The foliage is so thick that it could hide any number of dangers.

name: old armor
description: The armor is rusted and dented.

name: old weapon
description: The weapon is crafted from pure silver and shines from ample polishing.  It looks like a dagger with a fancy sheath.

name: old machinery lying around, rusting
description: The machinery is obviously no longer in working condition

name: cobwebs that appear to be everywhere
description: The cobweb forms a beautiful pattern.

name: mining carts
description: The mining cart has seen better days. It is old and battered.

name: hand cuffs
description: Cold metal cuffs that clang together loudly. You find yourself wondering who has been made to wear them before....

name: ornate inlay-ed floor decorations
description: The floor decoration is ornate.  The floor itself is made of stone tile.

name: outside of a castle
description: The castle is made of stone and overlooks a vast land.

name: stone that is ancient and antique with a shiny gloss of silver
description: The stone is round and smooth, as if it has been polished.

name: gardens
description: The aroma of the garden is relaxing and refreshing, with the plants giving off an assortment of various colors.

name: delightful flowers.
description: The flowers are bright and smell of fresh rain, as if they have come from a meadow.

name: stones used on the entrance door
description: The stone is covered in blood

name: drawbridge to the castle
description: The drawbridge is made of wood and metal.  It is large and wide.

name: plush velvet seats
description: The velvet seat is bright and colorful. It is easy on the eye.

name: screen
description: The screen is semi-transparent and has a few holes here and there.

name: wood stools
description: The stool is sturdy and made of wood.  The seat is made of leather.

name: alcohol tap
description: The tap is polished and golden and the beer flows freely from it.

name: cleaning cloth
description: Stained with dirt and grit, the cloth is losing its effectiveness.

name: stone bench
description: The stone benchis so sturdy and can last a lifetime.

name: cobblestone walkway
description: The walkway is made of smooth riverstones and you are impressed with the craftsmanship.

name: flowerpots
description: The ceramic flowerpot contains tulips picked from the outside garden

name: quaint manor
description: The manor is run-down and covered in vines. You wonder if it will reamain upright through the day.

name: rolling hills
description: What a green rolling hill, so many pink flowers grow on it and even some mushrooms

name: small stone fence
description: The fence is made from gray stones of different sizes. It's only a few feet high, so it can easily be climbed over.

name: home
description: The home is strong and sturdy from being built out of stone

name: bookshop
description: The bookshop is covered from floor to ceiling in full bookshelves, and the air of it filled with the scent of leather bindings and old paper.

name: rose bush
description: This rose Bush requires a lot of work. Looks like there are a couple of spider webs and there are no actual roses growing

name: small garden
description: The small garden is a favorite of the queen's - lined with the most ornate foliage.

name: white wooden gate
description: The sturdy white wooden gate towers 20 feet in the air, protecting the people of the village from all kinds of challengers.

name: steel statue
description: The steel statue looks like it has seen better days. It's all dirty and has marks all over it.

name: cauldron
description: The cauldron can be used for cooking vegetables

name: glass jars
description: The jar is glass.  It is dirty and has streaks.

name: spider legs
description: The pider leg is hairy and the sight of it makes you panic.

name: dragon toe nails
description: The dragon toe nails are covered in thick layers of red blood, the most recent layer appears to be very fresh and still has a pugent odor of iron that lingered heavily.

name: fairy wings
description: It is so light and almost transparent, with light shining through it.

name: scepter
description: On its handle, you see two red gems gleaming like eyes of an animal.

name: soft bed
description: This bed is very small but so ridiculously soft. It looks brand new which is weird because it's 245 years old

name: big rug
description: The big rug is soft to the touch.

name: big window
description: The glass of the big window is warped and difficult to see through. The streams in the glass appeared as if water frozen in place.

name: wardrobe
description: The wardrobe is made of high quality woods, intricate designs have been carved on its surface.

name: shackles on the wall
description: The shackle is rusted and dirty from holding many prisoners

name: knife
description: The knife is clean and well polished.

name: torture devices
description: The castle's dungeon is full of complicated and painful torture devices for the King's prisoners.

name: plexi glass like clear structures
description: The structures are clear and brilliant.  They are made of a glass like material.

name: fireplace
description: The hot embers are glowing and an occasional spark leaps from the fireplace as you hear the crackle of the firewood burning.

name: pew bench
description: The pew was made of dark oak and was lined with red royal satin.

name: gilded mirrors
description: The large mirror is oval in shape. It is gilded around the edges.

name: handmade rug
description: The rug is decorated in a intricate striped pattern and is obviously the work of a fine craftsman.

name: tapestries lining the walls depicting past royalty
description: The tapestry is large and shows an image of a king giving a flower to a little girl.

name: goblets
description: This goblet is made out of high quality glass. Some initials are engraved on the side

name: fur skin rug
description: This fur skin rug used to be in a hunter's bedroom. It's made out of a brown bear

name: beaten copper pot
description: The copper pot shows years of use, with the copper color beginning to warp on the handle. There are dents throughout the body as well.

name: broom
description: This broom has never seen dirt. The straws are perfect and unscathed.

name: curtains
description: The curtains were made from the best royal blue silk in the land and the Queen's initials were sewn into them.

name: chairs
description: the chair is royal in nature and has engravings and decor all over. it is clear only someone of worth is allowed to sit in it

name: cells
description: Oh what an old and screechy sell. Anybody can easily escape from it because the rods are so rusty , they can be easily broken

name: soaring ceiling painted with the richest cobalt blue and ruby red paints
description: The ceiling has the color red to represent the blood of the enemies and rich cobalt blue to represent the blue skies ahead.

name: gold statues
description: This is a gold statue of a Siberian husky.

name: calm water fountain
description: The fountain is large and round. It has carvings of fish on it.

name: paintings of gods
description: The painting has fiery colors and rough texture.

name: big ornate doors
description: The door is made of a beautiful, bright wood, and it is covered in carvings of trees and animals.

name: wooden counters
description: The counter was messy and reeked of a foul stench.

name: stone oven
description: An oven made of stone. Used for baking and keeping warm.

name: pot
description: The pot is old and cracked, with rust covering the outside.

name: tool
description: The tool has a metal surface and is very shiny.

name: cupboard
description: The cupboard is filled with all manner of dishware, its handles long worn down from constantly being opened and closed.

name: silverware
description: The silverware was well taken care of and maintained it's shine

name: vegetable or plant
description: This plant is long and hard, growing in a field. It is only edible when boiled.

name: low grass
description: The grass, no doubt, required many sheep to keep it low.

name: cloth sacks
description: The stained cloth sack has holes cut out for arms to fit through.

name: big table
description: The table is large enough for 50 people.

name: empty mug
description: The mug has been used for tea for a very long time.

name: faded letters
description: The letter is written on yellowed parchment paper. Each individual letter formed of a soft black undertone.

name: shelves
description: The shelf is made of dark rough-hewn wood and is large enough to hold several books or bowls.

name: staggering variety of wares
description: This looks to be a shallow brass bowl, carved with a motif of intertwining leaves on it.  It looks more decorative than useful.

name: shop counter
description: The oak counter looks well polished, the better display the many wares upon.  The wooden surface is inlaid with a set of scales in beech wood.

name: money register
description: The register is complex.  It has several buttons and keys.

name: carvings
description: The carving is deep and consists of several words in another language.

name: designed covers.
description: The designed covers look worn from use.

name: carpets
description: A decorative tapestry placed on the floor. Stylized and decorative.

name: gold and silver sculptures
description: The sculpture shines brightly. A gleaming testament to the material it embodies.

name: tomb
description: The tomb is filled with cobwebs. It has a dank, musty smell, and water dripped from the walls.

name: wrought iron chandelier
description: The chandelier is heavy and foreboding.  The black wrought iron portends of calamity ahead.

name: wooden doors
description: These doors appear quite study, and are hand crafted from oak. While they look quite old, they are well polished and cared for despite years of use.

name: kitchen
description: The kitchen shows how much power resides in everyday actions.

name: meals
description: The meal was amouthwatering roasted chicken with cheese and bread as the sides.

name: cooking pot
description: A large bellied vessel for making vast portions of hearty stews, and boiling laundry.

name: riverbank
description: The riverbank looks steep and hard to cross.

name: snapping turtles
description: This turtle looks quite disgruntled and discontented with life.  Perhaps you'd best steer clear of it.

name: broken logs
description: The broken logs would make great firewood.

name: broken weapons
description: This pike was broken in half at some point, and its point appears to be quite dull and rusty.

name: skulls
description: Broken and battered, the skull is a reminder for those who dare trespass.

name: waterfall
description: The waterfall flows over the side of the rock.  It is very cool water that is blue in color.

name: treasure
description: When you look at it closer, you see there is a missing part, like a gem had been removed from it.

name: pot of gold
description: The pot of gold is completely empty.  The rust on it shows it has not been full for quite some time.

name: primitive fishing pole
description: The fishing pole was splintered and worn.

name: hatchet
description: The hatchet is old and worn out.

name: pin
description: The pin is missing some stones but the clasp still works perfectly.

name: cottage roof
description: The roof looks sturdy enough.

name: hand plow
description: the hand plow is used for farming the fresh earth

name: bucket
description: The bucket is wooden, with a rope handle. It is starting to crack on one side.

name: filth from the kingdom
description: The filth is disgusting to look at and smells like rotten corpses

name: trash bags
description: The bag is full of stench and blood.

name: ornate table
description: The table is ornately carved and polished to a shine.

name: goblet
description: The goblet is made of metal and has a handle.

name: product
description: This product is unque and a great peice of art.

name: crates
description: This crate looks to be made of leftover wood scraps, as it looks like it is barely holding together.  Hopefully it does not need to travel very far.

name: sand for the cacti
description: You see some movement like something is moving around just below the surface.

name: tools for keeping the cacti trimmed
description: Tools for keeping the cacti trimmed are necessary for any farmer of the desert.

name: cold stone walls
description: the cold stone wall has several indents but still appears sturdy. you would not bet on your ability to break through it if necessary

name: corridors
description: The corridors looked vast and empty.

name: kingdom
description: The kingdom spans many miles, its stone structures standing in stark contrast to the grasslands around it.

name: secret tunnel
description: The tunnel is cold and damp.  It is hard to see in the tunnel.

name: instrument of torture
description: There are several instruments of torture that can be used to gain information.

name: dunes
description: The dunes are massive, and have many strange animals living in them.

name: cobblestone
description: A stone often used to pave roads. Found in rivers. Water over the millenniums has worn away any sharp edges.

name: thick water
description: The water is dark and murky. Drinking it would be dangerous.

name: copper
description: Look at all that copper, they could make a lot of pennies with that.

name: corn
description: The corn is tasty and delicious, it is big and vast.

name: sheep
description: The sheep is fluffy and healthy looking, it is and chewing its grass happily in the sun.

name: farm tools
description: The farm tools look like they could use an update.

name: food storage
description: The food storage is dark inside and cool, it's sealed door keeping the light from leaking in.

name: dozens and dozens of brim fish
description: The fish had a beautiful shine of red, radiating from it's scales.

name: irregular rocks
description: The rock stands as high as a dog and is probably too heavy to lift. However, with its smooth top, it does make a good seat.

name: lush green vegetation
description: The plant is lush and well kept and remains fruitful to this day.

name: tall pine trees
description: The tall pine trees towered overhead, and the wind blew through their branches.

name: clothes
description: This clothing piece is a worn linen shirt.  It looks like it might have been dyed green originally... or maybe brown... it's hard to tell.

name: water pail
description: The pail had rust on it's handle and there was a hole rusted through the bottom.

name: roots
description: The root grew so fast, you can see leaves starting to grow on it.

name: old tools
description: The tools are worn, showing their age, but still just as effective as the day they were welded.

name: wooden barriers
description: The barrier is sturdy and strong. It will please the King to have such a powerful defense.

name: barred windows
description: The window is covered in thick bars, so no one can get in or out.

name: papers
description: The paper is disheveled and frayed along the edges.  It has a tattered look about it as though it has not been moved in decades.

name: old rusty cashier's box
description: The box is covered in rust and dirt.

name: sewage
description: The drainage system in the kingdom is mediocre and the raw fresh sewage is smelled throughout the kingdom.

name: sculptures
description: The sculpture is a bust of a king of old, stern faced and with an elaborate crown that adorned his head.

name: wooden walls
description: the wall is plastered white

name: pillars
description: The pillar stands tall.

name: pastel sky
description: The sky is filled with soft and delicate pastel colors.

name: large pillars
description: The large pillar is made out of solid marble.  A closer look at the surface reveals the intricately engraved names of fallen war heroes.

name: drawings
description: The dusty drawing contains smudged legends leading to treasures in far-off lands.

name: entrance doors
description: The entrance doors to the castle are handcarved and adorned with gemstones and precious metals.

name: holy water
description: The holy water is a clear blue, and had a calming hue that radiated off of it.

name: weaponry
description: Instruments of power, adorned with sharp spiky things. A fighter's best friend.

name: peasants
description: the peasants wear rugged clothes and smell really bad. They hardly take a bath or brush their hair.

name: pelicans
description: The pelican is sitting there daring anyone to hurt it.

name: flies buzzing around
description: The fly buzzing around is irritating. Its fat body bumbling about as it makes its annoying noise nonstop.

name: cement
description: The cement is of the highest quality for the castle that will be built later.

name: cup
description: the cup is red in color.

name: pole
description: the pole is long

name: ale bottles
description: The bottle itself is old and covered with a layer of grime.  The ale inside however is well aged and prime for drinking.

name: pewter tankards
description: The tankard tapers small toward the top with a single handle. Looking at it the embossed symbols are very detailed.

name: candles
